content: I'll definitely check out those websites. I'm particularly interested in Zazzle and CafePress since they seem to offer a wide range of customizable products. I've had a good experience with Etsy, but it's always good to explore other options. By the way, I just remembered that I also bought a pair of concert tickets from Ticketmaster's website about 3 weeks ago for a show that's happening next month. I'm really excited for that.
